NFL Cleaning Services has been established since 1991 in the cleaning industry. NFL is a fully licensed and insured cleaning company that provides domestic and commercial cleaning services to both private and commercial clients.

We are a professional, friendly and a cost effective company with an excellent reputation. Over the past 25+ years we have developed a first class reputation in both contract commercial cleaning services and residential cleaning services with a focus on providing top notch service in relation to all of your cleaning requirements. All work is completed by the company owners, there is never anyone else sent to service your home or facility.

This is NOT ANOTHER FRANCHISE! We are locally owned and family operated and have been in business for over 25 years! We've made cleaning of every variety, from residences to office buildings to factories and restaurants, our life's work! Give us a call today and see what a difference we can make for you.
